dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"希望可以制裁埋狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999e919bc41244134c0671b3fd5e8c3b775b38d","tid":1510466,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a95067c8cf7f7c63e2e3cd8df53f3152c0c1443e","tid":1510466,"uid":29666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"正經post, 做實事<br />\n我地可以點聯絡Congress?<br />\n<br />\n直接email Marco Rubio?"}]}